metadata.dc:description: In this review we present an update on the anatomy and vascularization of the male urethra. The real objective of this review is to make the following chapters more understandable, both to know the physio-pathological mechanisms of urethral pathology and also to help us in their surgical management.
metadata.dc:title: Anatomia y vascularizacion de la uretra y el pene.
[Anatomy and vascularization on the male urethra and penis].
